{"tid":1355076,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸人翻墻係我地文宣的好時機","createTime":"2019-07-23T08:59:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T06:11:29.000Z","uid":201512,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4ff5afe425268d6e99c68fd58a966f8b44938f2d","tid":1355076,"uid":201512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:59:20.000Z","msg":"大家千奇唔好浪費唇舌同佢地辯論，因為你越爭論，<span style=\"color: red;\">佢地就越氣憤越愛國越係要揾理由去維護共產黨</span>，呢個係人人都有的反叛意識。<br />\n相反，我地可以好好利用呢個接觸大陸人的機會，不停<span style=\"color: red;\">散播謠言、分化佢地</span>。例如是<span style=\"color: red;\">食品安全</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">災後賑災物資被貪沒</span>，高官的<span style=\"color: red;\">國外資產，高官在外的親戚家眷</span>，甚至是<span style=\"color: red;\">大量不利中國的經濟消息</span>，鼓勵佢地走資。<br />\n然而，並非所有不利消息可以用來宣傳。失敗例子:六四、新疆再教育營。<span style=\"color: red;\">任何關於領土主權、人權、少數民族的事件都不適宜用作分化</span>，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">支那人根本唔覺得沒民主人權係問題，甚至支持逼害少數民族</span><br />\n歡迎大家一齊討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b459076f6fa03c10e047a63c8dad27ea39794b89","tid":1355076,"uid":201512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:00:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6d7fd6923b67c7943e23b99bc671ec328dcaf846","tid":1355076,"uid":201512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:03:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4cb543ae8190f8013f665d1af545d2f77664f51b","tid":1355076,"uid":201512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:05:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"aa10cd1e3f96a6e5929bbce87ddf68c00a10f0a1","tid":1355076,"uid":148385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:11:29.000Z","msg":"支持，建議整個懶人包，照copy and paste"}]}